==''Kerrang!'' Awards==
The [[Kerrang! Awards|''Kerrang!'' Awards]] is an annual awards ceremony held by ''[[Kerrang!]]'', a British [[rock music|rock]] magazine.  Nine Inch Nails has won two awards.

{{awards table}}
|-
| align="center"| 2005
| Nine Inch Nails
| Classic Songwriter Award<ref name="Kerrang songwriter" />
| {{won}}
|-
| align="center"| 2007
| Nine Inch Nails
| Kerrang! Icon Award<ref name="Kerrang icon" />
|{{won}}
{{end}}

